title: Ajnabee
subTitle: Raj and Priya befriend their new neighbours Vicky and Sonia. One day, Raj wakes up in Vicky's house and finds out that Sonia is killed and he is framed for it.

title: Dhanwaan
subTitle: Kashinath and Imli love each other. However, things take a turn when a wealthy woman, Anjali, meets Kashinath and falls in love with him, whereas Imli reveals that she suffers from a heart ailment.

title: Kya Yehi Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Rahul falls in love with Sandhya, a fellow college student, but realises that she does not reciprocate his feelings. Undeterred by her rejection, he still pursues her but pays a huge price for it.

title: Action Jackson
subTitle: After falling love with a clumsy girl, a small-time goon comes in contact with his doppelganger, AJ, before setting off on a romantic journey with his ladylove.

title: Amar Akbar Anthony
subTitle: Three brothers, each raised in different religious households, reunite after many years in a chance encounter. They set out to take revenge on those responsible for separating them.

title: Kuch Kuch Hota Hai
subTitle: After reading the letter her mother had written for her before she died, Anjali decides to bring together her widowed father, Rahul, with his true love who is also named Anjali.

title: Kunwara
subTitle: Raju and Urmila fall deeply in love and vow to reunite in India. However, complications arise when Raju agrees to pose as Sharmila's husband before her family.

title: Suryavanshi
subTitle: An archaeologist digs up a secret underground palace, much to the dismay of the locals, who fear the consequences.

title: Hulchul
subTitle: A man and a woman come from two feuding families and pretend to be in love for revenge. Their plan goes awry when they fall in love and they must work on bringing together their families.

title: Hulchul

title: D-Day
subTitle: Intelligence officer Wali Khan and a team of highly-trained officers are set to nab Goldman, one of India's most wanted terrorists. However, their mission is threatened by a minor miscalculation.

title: Mandi
subTitle: Rukmini Bai runs a brothel that is visited by some of the most prominent men in the society. However, when one of the prostitutes has an illicit affair, the establishment is put at risk.

title: Daata
subTitle: A decorated school teacher's life is upended by devastating rumours, which ultimately leads to his death. His son Kundan now seeks vengeance.

title: M.S. Dhoni: The Untold Story
subTitle: M S Dhoni, a boy from Ranchi, aspires to play cricket for India. Though he initially tries to please his father by working for the Indian Railways, he ultimately decides to chase his dreams.

title: Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Durga, who is blind, loses her fiance, Rohit, while she is getting her eye surgery. As she copes with her pain, she finds solace in Raj but chaos ensues when Rohit returns from the dead.

title: Main Tera Hero
subTitle: Seenu and Sunaina fall in love after he saves her from a violent policeman. However, their love story takes a turn when a gangster's daughter wants to marry Seenu.

title: Achanak
subTitle: A man is determined to prove his lover's innocence after she is suddenly accused of murdering his family.

title: Anth
subTitle: Kali, the son of a gangster, rapes and kills Pooja, and frames her fiance, who is killed in custody, for the crime. As a result, her brother, Vijay, vows revenge against Kali.

title: Aakhri Adalat
subTitle: An honest police officer decides to take the law into his own hands when he loses his job, and the thugs he caught get released due to some technicality.

title: Aladin
subTitle: Aladin, an orphan tormented by bullies, discovers a magic lamp that grants him incredible powers. Later, with the help of a genie, he embarks on thrilling adventures to defeat the evil Ringmaster.

title: Dillagi
subTitle: Ranvir and Rajvir, two inseparable brothers, support each other through thick and thin. However, they find themselves in a dilemma when both of them fall in love with the same woman.

title: Hera Pheri
subTitle: Vijay and Ajay make a living by stealing money from people. Their friendship is affected when Vijay discovers that Ajay's father may have been his father's killer.

title: Devdas
subTitle: After his wealthy family prohibits him from marrying the woman he is in love with, Devdas's life spirals downward as he takes up alcohol and a life of vice to alleviate the pain.

title: Yeshwant
subTitle: Yeshwant, an honest police inspector, is framed and arrested for a murder. However, after being released from prison, he learns that his wife is having an affair.

title: Khuda Gawah
subTitle: Badshah Khan travels to India to behead the man who killed Benazir's father and win her hand in marriage. He succeeds in his mission but is caught by Ranveer Singh, a jailor.

title: Hum
subTitle: A man is determined to kill a cruel businessman to get revenge for his father's death but is stopped by an inspector who is the mastermind behind the troubles.
